    <h4>The Difference Between a Multivariate Test and an A/B Test</h4>
    <div class="grid12 center">
      <h5 class="a-center">What is the difference between A/B testing and a multivariate testing? Let's take a look at the methodology, common uses, advantages, and limitations of these testing methods.</h5>
